android.car.diagnostic

类 CarDiagnosticEvent.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.diagnostic.CarDiagnosticEvent.Builder
  • 封闭类:
    CarDiagnosticEvent

    public static class CarDiagnosticEvent.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class can be used to incrementally construct a CarDiagnosticEvent. CarDiagnosticEvent instances are immutable once built.
